Project is developed in layers [layers architecture ]
--------------------------------------------------


A project is develope dusing a layered architecture
every layer is independent .
  
	UI 	    ------>          	 Presentation      		------>		       Service layer   	------>	       Integration Layer     	------>	     	DAO Layer    ------> 			     DB layer
          <------															  	<------                           <------         (optional)            <------                     <------
